data.description: Located in sought-after PGA Verano, this 2 bed/2 bath home offers luxury living with unparalleled amenities. Greeted by a bright & airy floor plan, you'll find a welcoming living area & a flex room that can be used as an office, den, or third bedroom. The chef's kitchen boasts quartz countertops, 42'' shaker cabinets, & ample storage space. The master bedroom features his & hers closets & a spa-like bathroom with dual vanities. The backyard includes a screened-in lanai, fenced-in yard, & plenty of room for a pool. This gated community offers a multitude of amenities such as a resort-style pool, social clubhouse, fitness center, 27 pickleball courts, & noteworthy golf courses. With all the luxuries this exceptional residence has to offer, don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
